Two lawmakers have clashed over ongoing campaigns to succeed Governor Wycliffe Oparanya. Lugari MP Ayub Savula and his Mumias East counterpart Benjamin Washiali differed in public over whether those eyeing the governor's seat should start campaigning. ALSO READ:

